{"id":146092,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/中国将关闭“不符合办报办刊规定”出版物/","date":"2011-04-20T17:31:41Z","modified":"2011-04-20T17:31:41Z","title":"中国将关闭“不符合办报办刊规定”出版物","content":"<p>官方媒体《中国青年报》报导，中国的报刊出版单位在五年将减至五千家，加大舆论引导作用。 新闻出版总署透露，今后5年将退出停办一批规模小实力弱的出版单位，退出停办一批资质差、资不抵债、发展能力不足、不符合国家有关办报办刊规定的报刊出版单位；通过兼并、整合、重组推进报刊出版骨干企业和传媒集团建设；引导支持拥有一定品牌效应和细分市场前景的中小型报刊出版单位走内涵发展道路，培育现代报刊出版企业，形成富有活力、差异化竞争的优势产业群。将重点扶持中央主要报刊，发挥在舆论传播中引领和主导作用，建立报刊公共服务机制和体系，大力推进党和国家重点报刊多媒体、多业态发展&#8230;.<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/144f2555/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%86%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%8A%9E%E6%8A%A5%E5%8A%9E%E5%88%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E2%80%9D%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%89%A9&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F20%2F0252252%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%86%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%90%88%E5%8A%9E%E6%8A%A5%E5%8A%9E%E5%88%8A%E8%A7%84%E5%AE%9A%E2%80%9D%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E7%89%A9&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F04%2F20%2F0252252%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100752055005/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/144f2555/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/100752055005/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/144f2555/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=LNLy7WNVZFg:qHfFYEuvSAE:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds